snippet.title: Little Island Adventure — Gameplay testing (rowing boats)
snippet.description:
Gameplay testing for the Little Island Adventure game. 

We’ve got the mood for blue skies, sunshine, & adventure today!

This video is a compilation of in-game footage and it’s currently in the pre-alpha stage, so stay tuned to see more updates!
